{"tid":947280,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我好似鍾意左公司個女同事 但係呢段關係唔會有得開始","createTime":"2018-12-19T07:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T08:40:50.000Z","uid":183389,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d2e302ae2db35735e1cc8e691351966d78e5d7a","tid":947280,"uid":183389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:11:05.000Z","msg":"我小薯黎<br />\n隔離組有個女同事 係到做左好耐<br />\n仔都生埋<br />\n我覺得佢好有自信 好知道自己做緊咩 係office 算係會打扮 雖然已經4字頭 但係仲有一顆少女心 都算跟得上潮流 聽歌食野都有品味<br />\n有時候我好迷茫搵佢都可以指點到我<br />\n<br />\n結果過左幾個禮拜之後 <br />\n我又普通同事變仰慕<br />\n然後依家每日都會留意她行過 <br />\n她係我附近同其他人講野 我都會不自覺分心聽她講嘢 她放假我就會好心不在焉 無乜動力<br />\n<br />\n有時放工我都會特登扮偶遇同路 跟著問一唔一齊食d野<br />\n<br />\n呢段關係其實只有我自己維繫，我想忘記同控制自己，可以點樣？"},{"pid":"fec2eb5a76f0fa4f32e0ac35727262c6e4ecc918","tid":947280,"uid":7507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:13:13.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去......."},{"pid":"6d5d368e43e82232d6e7804f4f323f04774cd1e8","tid":947280,"uid":225871,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"4字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c81e391c1c126455ed40b29ddcb1eda00c41202","tid":947280,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:16:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f49ca41e880d1427ec3508b3a407d1bb6b7bc55f","tid":947280,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"耆齡王啲Friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c06313ffebe25cca5438bcb090e76633ecfab6","tid":947280,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"做得你阿姐喎"},{"pid":"43de9da74d1dd2137c0b0cb08f2fa97db0954fda","tid":947280,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/deb/7b4/deb7b4e21071ed9